{"trip_id":"2015-france-laon-vezelay-burgundy-puy-en","epigraph":{"quote":"Corners of towers cut away, so platforms for cows to look out."},"moments":[{"seq":2,"place_id":"stalisfield-kent-uk","lon":0.812558,"lat":51.2442782,"place":"Stalisfield, Kent, UK","date":"2015-07-25","role":"overnight_base","quote":"As soon as we arrived I put the kettle on (5.10.) + then did yoga for 10 min + felt much less stiff.","images":[]},{"seq":3,"place_id":"folkestone-eurotunnel-uk","lon":1.1294595,"lat":51.0952567,"place":"Folkestone (Eurotunnel), UK","date":"2015-07-25","role":"crossing_terminal","quote":"Sunday We set off at 8.45. & reached the Channel Tunnel car park at 9.10. An hour early, but yesterday queues had been 5 hrs.","images":[]},{"seq":4,"place_id":"suzy-aisne-france","lon":3.4566822,"lat":49.5588188,"place":"Suzy, Aisne, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"overnight_base","quote":"Camping in wagons & tipis. Nice.","images":[]},{"seq":5,"place_id":"laon-france","lon":3.620686,"lat":49.564665,"place":"Laon, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"main_stop","quote":"Laon Cathedral is beautiful, especially the Tower of the crossing from inside!","images":[{"src":"media/2015-france-laon-vezelay-burgundy-puy-en/B_0253_L_1.webp","w":867,"h":900,"caption":"Laon","type":"postcard"}]},{"seq":6,"place_id":"trainel-aube-france","lon":3.4390462,"lat":48.4158765,"place":"Trainel, Aube, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"overnight_base","quote":"We drove thro the Laonnaise hills, skirting Champagne, then crossed a series of rivers such as Aisne, Marne + Seine on Droats.","images":[{"src":"media/2015-france-laon-vezelay-burgundy-puy-en/B_0253_R_1.webp","w":755,"h":900,"caption":"Suchard Lait chocolate wrapper","type":"ticket"}]},{"seq":7,"place_id":"vezelay-france","lon":3.746285,"lat":47.4657306,"place":"Vézelay, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"main_stop","quote":"At one time 1000 pilgrims were burned when the cathedral caught fire.","images":[{"src":"media/2015-france-laon-vezelay-burgundy-puy-en/B_0254_L_1.webp","w":837,"h":900,"caption":"Vézelay on Yonne","type":"postcard"}]},{"seq":8,"place_id":"chaumot-nievre-france","lon":3.64661,"lat":47.25631,"place":"Chaumot, Nièvre, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"overnight_base","quote":"Sodden cyclists keep arriving...","images":[{"src":"media/2015-france-laon-vezelay-burgundy-puy-en/B_0256_L_1.webp","w":900,"h":522,"caption":"Paray-le-Monial — Christ in Glory","type":"postcard"},{"src":"media/2015-france-laon-vezelay-burgundy-puy-en/B_0256_L_2.webp","w":554,"h":580,"caption":"Paray-le-Monial — North Portal","type":"postcard"},{"src":"media/2015-france-laon-vezelay-burgundy-puy-en/B_0256_L_3.webp","w":579,"h":580,"caption":"Paray-le-Monial — Porche","type":"postcard"}]},{"seq":9,"place_id":"paray-le-monial-saone-et-loire-france","lon":4.1177959,"lat":46.450559,"place":"Paray-le-Monial, Saône-et-Loire, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"overnight_base","quote":"Simon didn't come into one of the most interesting churches with this theme because it had a \"no shorts\" sign.","images":[{"src":"media/2015-france-laon-vezelay-burgundy-puy-en/B_0257_L_1.webp","w":759,"h":900,"caption":"Saint Jean-Saint Maurice sur Loire","type":"photo"}]},{"seq":10,"place_id":"saint-jean-saint-maurice-sur-loire-france","lon":4.0035922,"lat":45.9661145,"place":"Saint-Jean-Saint-Maurice-sur-Loire, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"main_stop","quote":"There were 2 layers of mist on the reservoir.","images":[]},{"seq":11,"place_id":"saint-paul-de-vezelin-loire-france","lon":4.085008,"lat":45.8845401,"place":"Saint-Paul-de-Vézelin, Loire, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"overnight_base","quote":"We have now reached a v. entertaining one, bursting with noisy children.","images":[]},{"seq":12,"place_id":"saint-etienne-france","lon":4.3873058,"lat":45.4401467,"place":"Saint-Étienne, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"transit_stop","quote":"We drove off from the Gorges of the Loire south. Bigger hills, [Saw] past St Etienne.","images":[]},{"seq":13,"place_id":"saint-maurice-de-lignon-haute-loire-france","lon":4.1375076,"lat":45.2230922,"place":"Saint-Maurice-de-Lignon, Haute-Loire, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"transit_stop","quote":"Simon bought lunch in St. Maurice de Lignon + stopped soon after in a village ringed round a huge green.","images":[]},{"seq":14,"place_id":"la-besse-haute-loire-france","lon":4.1269996,"lat":45.1719724,"place":"La Besse, Haute-Loire, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"transit_stop","quote":"Men are dismantling a village marquee after yesterday's festival.","images":[]},{"seq":15,"place_id":"brives-charensac-haute-loire-france","lon":3.92197,"lat":45.0474,"place":"Brives-Charensac, Haute-Loire, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"overnight_base","quote":"Every pedal + push, steady incline. Only 1½ hours to get back, free-wheeling nearly all the way.","images":[{"src":"media/2015-france-laon-vezelay-burgundy-puy-en/B_0259_L_2.webp","w":830,"h":386,"caption":"Allotments with rocky butte behind","type":"photo"},{"src":"media/2015-france-laon-vezelay-burgundy-puy-en/B_0259_R_1.webp","w":900,"h":664,"caption":"Town square with Romanesque church facade and crowd","type":"photo"},{"src":"media/2015-france-laon-vezelay-burgundy-puy-en/B_0259_R_2.webp","w":900,"h":856,"caption":"Below the Holy Cross sanctuary, recumbent stone effigy","type":"postcard"}]},{"seq":16,"place_id":"entraygues-sur-truyere-aveyron-france","lon":2.56605,"lat":44.6432147,"place":"Entraygues-sur-Truyère, Aveyron, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"overnight_base","quote":"Late, about 8.30, we walked up into town & saw trestle tables & lots of people eating in the square & local produce on sale.","images":[{"src":"media/2015-france-laon-vezelay-burgundy-puy-en/B_0260_R_1.webp","w":752,"h":306,"caption":"Hand-drawn old bridge with buttresses","type":"sketch"}]},{"seq":17,"place_id":"conques-aveyron-france","lon":2.3981666,"lat":44.5995543,"place":"Conques, Aveyron, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"main_stop","quote":"We chose a restaurant on the square which advertised puddings made in the restaurant. It was a very good choice.","images":[{"src":"media/2015-france-laon-vezelay-burgundy-puy-en/B_0261_L_1.webp","w":900,"h":525,"caption":"Abbatiale Sainte-Foy, tympan du Jugement dernier (début du XIIe siècle)","type":"postcard"},{"src":"media/2015-france-laon-vezelay-burgundy-puy-en/B_0261_R_1.webp","w":698,"h":612,"caption":"Abbey interior with Romanesque arches","type":"postcard"}]},{"seq":18,"place_id":"figeac-lot-france","lon":2.0324321,"lat":44.6092335,"place":"Figeac, Lot, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"main_stop","quote":"We drove to Figeac, looked at the Rosetta Stone, had good coffee in the covered market & shopped.","images":[]},{"seq":19,"place_id":"cajarc-lot-france","lon":1.8421185,"lat":44.486397,"place":"Cajarc, Lot, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"overnight_base","quote":"There is a pool, a lovely walnut orchard","images":[]},{"seq":20,"place_id":"treignac-correze-france","lon":1.7935339,"lat":45.5365916,"place":"Treignac, Corrèze, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"overnight_base","quote":"We had crepes & beer & swam in the lake.","images":[]},{"seq":21,"place_id":"montreuil-sur-mer-france","lon":1.7631125,"lat":50.4638918,"place":"Montreuil-sur-Mer, France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"overnight_base","quote":"When Simon opened it there was only her old passport inside it.","images":[]},{"seq":22,"place_id":"coquelles-eurotunnel-france","lon":1.7950055,"lat":50.9180426,"place":"Coquelles (Eurotunnel), France","date":"2015-07-25","role":"crossing_terminal","quote":"9:15. after David had signed some papers we left... Simon drove the whole way until we reached the Hermitage Hotel, Montreuil, 8.45 pm.","images":[]},{"seq":23,"place_id":"folkestone-eurotunnel-uk","lon":1.1294595,"lat":51.0952567,"place":"Folkestone (Eurotunnel), UK","date":"2015-07-25","role":"crossing_terminal","quote":"Simon drove the whole way until we reached the Hermitage Hotel, Montreuil, 8.45 pm.","images":[]}]}